               <p>I am a <rs id="t17810711-62-viclabel323" type="occupation">stay-maker</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17810711-62-victim783 t17810711-62-viclabel323"></join> at Croydon in Surry.<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="178107110148"></xptr> The prisoner took my watch from me upon the 17th of June. I was with Lee and 
