                  <interp inst="t17810711-62-crimeloc324" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t17810711-62-off321 t17810711-62-crimeloc324"></join>: we drank two or three pots of beer there; Mr. Anderson, and me, and the girls; and then we went home with them to 
               <persName id="t17810711-62-person786">
                  Margaret
                   Flynn
               <interp inst="t17810711-62-person786" type="surname" value="Flynn"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17810711-62-person786" type="given" value="Margaret"></interp>
